      "Created multiple AI systems (J.A.R.V.I.S., F.R.I.D.A.Y., E.D.I.T.H.)",
      "Developed nanotechnology for Iron Man suits",
      "Key figure in defeating Thanos and saving the universe"
    ]
  },
  "relationshipsAndSocialLife": {
    "significantRelationships": [
      {
        "name": "Virginia 'Pepper' Potts",
        "nature": "Wife, former assistant"
      }
